{"tid":1740922,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢發到攰，要去台灣差下電？幫大家整左少少資料整合","createTime":"2019-11-20T06:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T08:05:12.000Z","uid":258339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"69471cabb586ff2af48ad7c2fb6e1be847c60cc8","tid":1740922,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:16:32.000Z","msg":"［代post]到台灣留學<br />\n<br />\n有唔少台灣大學出左聲明，歡迎香港生以專案訪問、旁聽、國際生等等嘅形式到台灣進修下。以下有一張清單，列出七間有相關安排嘅台灣大學同埋佢哋嘅聯絡方法，歡迎尋找緊出國進修機會嘅你參考下。日後有更多台灣大學出聲明嘅話條list會再加長： <br />\nshorturl.at/yDRTW<br />\n<br />\n有個別大學更加講明能夠提供宿位，請大家係閱讀各間大學嘅聲明同資料嗰陣細心留意下。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"95f231c6d026a6049b312ac9760dae2abdc4c4bc","tid":1740922,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:17:16.000Z","msg":"P牌自推"},{"pid":"2b23984882f8ee38d788cc25598598c02c8df144","tid":1740922,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:17:48.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"d7d8766c4e58c5d7a63155b54501db7c17fd07ab","tid":1740922,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:18:21.000Z","msg":"1<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3d167193732481be5a5e507cb7a8807f1755b1","tid":1740922,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:18:39.000Z","msg":"2<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd10484a73a309630eb78bfee1c8b54985d7a8f4","tid":1740922,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:18:53.000Z","msg":"3<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b9d3c6cfa8714863ea555aa5f5e1ad90af2cde","tid":1740922,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:19:14.000Z","msg":"4<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b520000999e2c62f5ac13b02cdaf12656c401f36","tid":1740922,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike